nto Arena.\n\n    - Resolved an issue causing disconnects when transitioning from the lobby into a multiplayer match.\n\n    - Resolved a few issues with the Tutorial.\n\n    - General stability fixes to multiplayer horse to prevent stuck states.\n\nImprovements:\n\n    - Modified shooting assists for a better overall feel.\n\n    - Expanded multiplayer horse to allow up to 6 players.\n\n    - Improved AI decision making.\n\n    - Reduced the sitting height adjustment.\n\n    - Improved the fall animation when an AI is pushed.\n\n    - Art improvements throughout.\n\n    - Increased the smoothness of AI movements and behavior.\n\nNew Features:\n\n    - Is the game taking too long? You can now choose to play 2 minute quarters instead or keep the classic 3 minute quarters.\n\n    - Increased the aggressiveness of the AI by giving them the ability to steal.\n\n    - Players now become ghost spectators in multiplayer horse when they lose.", "created_date": 1732311686, "id": "8820549284673667", "version": "0.410", "version_code": 410, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6781908485204434", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8820549284673667"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1732216807, "id": "8814258178636111", "version": "0.409", "version_code": 409, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_applicatio